{{Infobox dungeon |name = Sprout Tower |image = [[File:Sprout Tower.png|300px]] |caption = An outside view of Sprout Tower. |tokens = 2,500 |location = Directly east of Violet City. }} '''Sprout Tower''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Johto]]. It has 36 tiles arranged in a 6x6 square, including 6 chest tiles, 15 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
